<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/global.css">
    <title>Professional Recipe Sharing Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include the header here -->
    <%- include("header.ejs") %>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-background"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="title">
                <h1>Welcome to <span style="color: yellow;">Recipe Sharing Page</span></h1>
                <p class="sub-title">Your ultimate taste experience awaits!!!</p>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-recipe">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <div class="about-details">
            <div class="about-description">
                <p>Welcome to Recipe Sharing, your go-to platform for discovering and sharing the best recipes from all over the world. Based in the vibrant city of London, we are passionate about bringing together food lovers from every corner of the globe.</p>
                <p>Our journey began in the heart of London, a city renowned for its diverse culinary scene. Inspired by the rich tapestry of flavors and cultures, Recipe Sharing was founded to celebrate this diversity and make it accessible to everyone. Whether you're a seasoned chef or a home cook, we invite you to join our community and share your culinary creations.</p>
                <p>At Recipe Sharing, we believe that food is a universal language that brings people together. Our platform allows you to explore new recipes, connect with fellow food enthusiasts, and showcase your own dishes. From traditional family recipes to modern twists on classic dishes, our community is a melting pot of culinary inspiration.</p>
                <p>We are thrilled to welcome food lovers from all cities to our platform. No matter where you're from, your recipes and stories are valued here. Together, let's create a space where everyone can discover new tastes and share the joy of cooking.</p>
                <p>Sincerely, The Recipe Sharing Team</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="images/Picture_4.avif" alt="About Food Picture">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="recipes-actions">
        <h2>Manage Recipes</h2>
        <div class="recipe-buttons">
            
            <button onclick="location.href='/recipes/add'" class="recipe-btn">Add Recipe</button>
            <!-- <button onclick="location.href='recipes/details'" class="recipe-btn">Recipe Details</button> -->
            <!-- <button onclick="location.href='/recipes/edit'" class="recipe-btn">Edit Recipe</button> -->
            <button onclick="location.href='/recipes/list'" class="recipe-btn">Recipes List</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
        <h2>Testimonials</h2>
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
            <div class="testimonial-item">
                <img src="images/picture_1.jpg" alt="Miss Conica">
                <p>"This platform has transformed my cooking experience. I've learned so much and connected with amazing chefs!"</p>
                <p>Miss Conica</p>
                <div class="rating">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
            <div class="testimonial-item">
                <img src="images/picture_1.jpg" alt="Mr. John Doe">
                <p>"A fantastic place to discover new recipes and share my own creations. Highly recommended!"</p>
                <p>Mr. John Doe</p>
                <div class="rating">★★★★☆</div>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
            <div class="testimonial-item">
                <img src="images/picture_1.jpg" alt="Mrs. Jane Smith">
                <p>"I love the variety of recipes available. There's always something new to try and enjoy!"</p>
                <p>Mrs. Jane Smith</p>
                <div class="rating">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial 4 -->
            <div class="testimonial-item">
                <img src="images/picture_1.jpg" alt="Mr. Alex Johnson">
                <p>"The community here is incredible. I've received so much positive feedback on my recipes!"</p>
                <p>Mr. Alex Johnson</p>
                <div class="rating">★★★★☆</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Recipe Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
